This branch is a testbed for exploring C++11/14 features.

This software provides ABSOLUTELY NO GUARANTEE that you will not brick or otherwise render your Valon inoperable if you use it, correctly or incorrectly.

User beware.

2016-01-06:
* Refactored C++ code to allow more flexibility in interfacing by using boost::asio.

2015-05-06:

* Added a means to set all the options present in the Valon configuration registers.
* Enabled checksum verification.
